title: Add catalyst "peer.decentraland.zone"
body:
> Discussion: [https://forum.decentraland.org/t/dao-proposal-add-catalyst-peer-decentraland-zone/677](https://forum.decentraland.org/t/dao-proposal-add-catalyst-peer-decentraland-zone/677)

Explain why this node should be added to the Catalyst network. Why would this addition be beneficial to the network? For example, adding nodes in new geographic areas helps to provide a better experience to more users.
